# identify subclasses at each clustering resolution
# do differential expression for clusters within each subclass
# generate plots of top genes for each

subclass.idx.opossum <- list()

subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1$Astro <- c("4", "6", "8", "9")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1.5$Astro <- c("5", "7", "9", "13", "14", "18")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.2$Astro <- c("6", "8", "11", "12", "16", "17", "22")

subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1$Micro <- c("5")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1.5$Micro <- c("6")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.2$Micro <- c("2")

subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1$OD <- c("1", "2", "7", "10", "12")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1.5$OD <- c("1", "3", "4", "8", "10", "11", "16")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.2$OD <- c("1", "3", "5", "7", "9", "10", "15", "18", "20")

subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1$OPC <- c("3", "13", "14")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1.5$OPC <- c("2", "12", "17", "19")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.2$OPC <- c("4", "13", "14", "21", "23")

subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1$Endo <- c("11")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1.5$Endo <- c("15")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.2$Endo <- c("19")

subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1$VLMC <- c("15")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.1.5$VLMC <- c("20")
subclass.idx.opossum$SCT_snn_res.2$VLMC <- c("24")

obj.opossum.nonneuronal <- SubclassByIdent(obj.opossum.nonneuronal, subclass.idx.opossum)


subclass.labels <- c("Astro", "OD", "OPC")
ident.labels <- c("SCT_snn_res.1", "SCT_snn_res.1.5", "SCT_snn_res.2")

markers.opossum.nonneuronal <- IdentMarkerDict(obj.opossum.nonneuronal, subclass.labels, ident.labels,
                                        "E:/Transcriptomics_V1/Opossum/seurat/marker_genes/Nonneuronal/markerdict_clusters.rds")
